precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 50 -
which (a) DECLARES the storm surge which occured in NEW BRUNSWICK on
October 29, 2000, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b)
AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance.
